{"id": "1197192587476475995", "channel_id": "1197192587476475995", "type": 0, "author_id": "1048973279500701797", "author_name": "nesoteric", "author_bot": false, "content": "本已不想再动笔，但诺谛拉忽地入梦。\n大抵是返航的故事罢，细节已记不清，却总觉眼含余泪。\n所以这副也算是记梦之作罢。\n但是梦啊，梦的画面已不甚清晰，已然难以复现那份苍凉与孤寂。\n\n草笔作画，一挥而就，无甚细节。\n无论怎样地刻画都是对梦的不忠实。\n也许完备的艺术，便是能忠于梦境的艺术。", "timestamp": "2024-01-17T14:55:55.617000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197192587975594014", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1447846, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197192587476475995/1197192587975594014/1.jpg?ex=69ff4afb&is=69fdf97b&hm=da243b9265dd3007d3979f2a5f6ada240ff615ec5312c64b4f35b9b37a59cf06&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197192587476475995", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "诺谛拉-返航", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537"]}
